In [28]:
n = len(iris_data['feature_names'])
for i in range(0, n - 1):
    for j in range(i + 1, n):
        plt.figure(figsize=(5, 5))
        scatter = plt.scatter(iris_data['data'][:, i],
                              iris_data['data'][:, j],
                              c=iris_data['target'], cmap='rainbow')
        plt.xlabel(iris_data['feature_names'][i])
        plt.ylabel(iris_data['feature_names'][j])
        plt.legend(handles=scatter.legend_elements()[0], title='Species',
                   labels=list(iris_data['target_names']))
        plt.show()
In [29]:
pca = PCA()
pca.fit(iris_data['data'])

iris_data['data_transformed'] = pca.transform(iris_data['data'])
In [30]:
n = len(iris_data['feature_names'])
for i in range(0, n - 1):
    for j in range(i + 1, n):
        plt.figure(figsize=(5, 5))
        scatter = plt.scatter(iris_data['data_transformed'][:, i],
                              iris_data['data_transformed'][:, j],
                              c=iris_data['target'], cmap='rainbow')
        plt.xlabel('PC' + str(i + 1))
        plt.ylabel('PC' + str(j + 1))
        plt.legend(handles=scatter.legend_elements()[0], title='Species',
                   labels=list(iris_data['target_names']))
        plt.show()
